@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(0.45)
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.43 / v0 + 0.85)) + wp.cos((v1 + 0.27 / v2 + 0.95)))
    tmp = 0.74
    v1 = (0.29 * ((v2 + 0.24 / v1 + 0.97) / 0.90))
    v1 = ((v2 / (v0 + 0.95 * v1 + 0.98)) * (v1 / (v1 + 0.46 / v1 + 0.84)))
    data[tid] = v0
